    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Krax Ca-caw’s Concoction Chaos is an arcade-style potion crafting game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286170/extras/05a2a4d0ad1ce704ed8e3a694c562b1e.avif?t=1732012911\" width=750 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have been accepted as the intern of master potion maker Krax Ca-caw. With him as your teacher, learn the intricate craft of potion brewery. Memorise the sacred magical recipe book, fill the cauldron with ingredients, and stir the mixture without letting the cauldron overflow. With this practice, you will be the next potion master in no time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>((Warning: this game contains imagery that may be harmful to players with photosensitive epilepsy or other similar conditions, if you experience any seizure symptoms IMMEDIATELY stop playing and consult a doctor.))</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286170/extras/c9132dc1f1c16a24b8e986570e0b813e.poster.avif?t=1732012911\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286170/extras/c9132dc1f1c16a24b8e986570e0b813e.webm?t=1732012911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286170/extras/c9132dc1f1c16a24b8e986570e0b813e.mp4?t=1732012911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mix a variety of magical potions!</strong> Pick from a variety of fantastical ingredients, stir the mixture in the cauldron, and make one of the many magical potions available in the game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play different game modes!</strong> Choose between three different game modes: high score, speedrun and endless.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose your own difficulty!  </strong>If standard difficulty isn't for you, you can choose from randomised recipe book pages. Or try blackout mode with reduced brightness.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
